fields.name: fy_start
fields.description: Start of applicable fiscal year range

fields.name: fy_end
fields.description: End of applicable fiscal year range

fields.name: EarlyRetElig_RetDate
fields.description: If plan member's date of retirement is on or after X... (EarlyRetElig_age/EarlyRetElig_tenure/EarlyRetElig_points)

fields.name: EarlyRetElig_age
fields.description: Plan member's age at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (EarlyRetElig_tenure/EarlyRetElig_points) to be eligible for early retirement.

fields.name: EarlyRetElig_tenure
fields.description: Plan member's tenure at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (EarlyRetElig_age/EarlyRetElig_points) to be eligible for early retirement.

fields.name: EarlyRetElig_points
fields.description: Plan member's age plus tenure at retirement must be X years or greater and satisfy (EarlyRetElig_age/EarlyRetElig_tenure) to be eligible for early retirement.

fields.name: EarlyRetElig_YrsfromNormRetElig
fields.description: Plan member must be within X years of normal retirement eligibility and satisfy (EarlyRetElig_age/EarlyRetElig_tenure/EarlyRetElig_points) to be eligible for early retirement.
